graph TB
    subgraph "Kubeflow Trainer Operator"
        Controller[trainer-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Validating Webhooks<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        TrainJobCtl[TrainJob Controller]
        RuntimeCtl[TrainingRuntime Controller]
        ClusterRuntimeCtl[ClusterTrainingRuntime Controller]
        ProgressTracker[Progression Tracker<br/>RHOAI Extension]
        NetPolicyMgr[Network Policy Manager<br/>RHOAI Extension]

        Controller --> TrainJobCtl
        Controller --> RuntimeCtl
        Controller --> ClusterRuntimeCtl
        Controller --> ProgressTracker
        Controller --> NetPolicyMgr
    end

    User[User/SDK] -->|creates| TrainJobCR[TrainJob CR]
    User -->|creates| RuntimeCR[TrainingRuntime CR]
    User -->|creates| ClusterRuntimeCR[ClusterTrainingRuntime CR]

    TrainJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    RuntimeCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    ClusterRuntimeCR -->|validated by| Webhook

    TrainJobCR -->|watched by| TrainJobCtl
    RuntimeCR -->|watched by| RuntimeCtl
    ClusterRuntimeCR -->|watched by| ClusterRuntimeCtl

    TrainJobCtl -->|creates| JobSet[JobSet]
    TrainJobCtl -->|creates| PodGroup[PodGroup<br/>Volcano/Coscheduling]
    JobSet -->|creates| TrainingPods[Training Pods<br/>Distributed Workload]

    ProgressTracker -->|polls HTTP| TrainingPods
    NetPolicyMgr -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy]
    NetworkPolicy -->|restricts| TrainingPods

    TrainJobCtl -->|depends on| JobSetController[JobSet Controller]
    TrainJobCtl -.->|optional| VolcanoScheduler[Volcano Scheduler]
    TrainJobCtl -.->|optional| Kueue[Kueue]

    TrainingPods -->|stores to| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring] -->|scrapes 8080/TCP| Controller

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ProgressTracker fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NetPolicyMgr fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrainJobCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ClusterRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style JobSetController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style VolcanoScheduler fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Kueue fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
